  "doc_id": "32914",
  "text": "The intrinsic kinetics of bacterial inactivation as a result of exposure to UV radiation are a function of the UV-C dose, expressed as the product of germicidal radiation intensity (I ) and exposure time (t). Several mathematical relationships have been developed to describe bacterial responses to UV irradiation. UV dose plays an important role in all bacterial inactivation models for UV irradiation [CITATION_1] .",
